show.description: Ten years after an injustice was committed, he vows to take revenge. His mentor, encouraging him to forget hatred and embrace love, suggests a marriage alliance. Unexpectedly becoming the son-in-law of a famous family, he ultimately defeats his enemies. Discover how he achieved this victory.
